marketing support.

Commodore will implement a Europe-wide  training programme for distributors and
sales staff, to promote  a high  level of  technical and product knowledge that
will equip them to deliver the best advice to customers.

Good after-sales service is equally vital to Commodore's customers.  As part of
our  philosophy to  make things  as easy  as possible  for them, we introduce a
range of service options.

In  summary,  ladies  and  gentlemen,  we  will  provided  clear   channels  of
distribution for  Commodore and  with  them  an unrivalled  package  of  price,
support and service.  We will make a success  of the still strong Commodore and
